    <item>
      <title>特朗普称其总统任期内不会建造风力发电场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-says-he-wants-no-wind-turbines-built-during-administration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普周二表示，他将在第二任期内推行不建造风电场的政策，这将对价值数十亿美元的风电项目计划造成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-says-he-wants-no-wind-turbines-built-during-administration</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 17:37:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称北约国家应将 GDP 的 5% 用于国防</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-says-nato-nations-should-spend-5-of-gdp-on-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[候任总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，北约国家应该将相当于其经济产出的 5% 用于国防，他对欧洲盟友的要求是目前目标的两倍以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-says-nato-nations-should-spend-5-of-gdp-on-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 17:37:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佛罗里达州美国法官阻止特别检察官提交特朗普报告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/florida-judge-blocks-release-of-special-counsel-s-trump-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州一名联邦法官阻止司法部发布针对唐纳德·特朗普的两项刑事调查报告，这可能导致这位当选总统与调查他的检察官之间发生法律纠纷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/florida-judge-blocks-release-of-special-counsel-s-trump-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 17:01:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管政府暂停征收资本利得税，加拿大仍将实施资本利得税改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/canada-to-apply-capital-gains-tax-change-despite-government-halt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多暂停议会，但加拿大税务机关将继续适用更高的资本利得纳入税率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/canada-to-apply-capital-gains-tax-change-despite-government-halt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 15:39:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国减少网络内容 暴力极端主义依然猖獗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/us-pulls-back-from-disrupting-violent-extremism-on-social-media</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据现任和前任美国官员以及互联网极端主义专家称，美国联邦调查局和国土安全部在过去两年中已经减少了打击暴力极端分子网络活动的力度，他们担心在即将上任的特朗普政府领导下，这种趋势将会加速。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/us-pulls-back-from-disrupting-violent-extremism-on-social-media</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 15:37:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登设立两座新国家纪念碑，保护 848,000 英亩土地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/biden-protects-848-000-acres-by-creating-two-national-monuments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据白宫称，总统乔·拜登正在建立两座新的国家纪念碑，以保护加利福尼亚州 848,000 英亩的土地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/biden-protects-848-000-acres-by-creating-two-national-monuments</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
